<solution>
<p><ul><li>4.4997600622571</li></ul></p><p><m>\displaystyle{P}{\left({t}\right)}={650}{e}^{{{0.05}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{814}={650}{e}^{{{0.05}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{814}}{{650}}={e}^{{{0.05}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{\ln{{\left(\frac{{814}}{{650}}\right)}}}={0.05}{t}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{\ln{{\left(\frac{{814}}{{650}}\right)}}}}{{0.05}}={t}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{t}={4.4997600622571}</m></p>
</solution>
